Ronda Blaylock was just 14-years-old in 1980 when she was found stabbed to death and brutally assaulted in Rural Hall, North Carolina . 
  She and a friend had taken a ride home from a man after school and her body was found three days later in a wooded area . 
  The man who gave her the ride was never found but police believe he still lives in the area and they are close to finding him . 
  Ronda was found after she was violently assaulted and stabbed . 
 